And from what everyone is saying here, Agema had enough to engage (one group), had the turtle being pulled first, and even got it to camp and engaged first.  So WHY did Prism even BEGIN to attack said turtle &quot;at all&quot;? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ucronuus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cronuus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(8/2/02 2:14:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1804.topic&index=21>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://mm-tn01.sac2.fastsearch.net/thumbnail?cmd=key&param=1402775 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ..</span><hr size=1> If a mob is being kited its not engaged,<br>
